'''Azincourt''' ({{IPA-fr|azɛ̃kuʁ}}; historically, '''Agincourt''' {{IPAc-en|ˈ|æ|ʒ|ɪ|n|k|ʊ|r}} in English) is a [[Commune of France|commune]] in the [[Pas-de-Calais]] [[Departments of France|department]] in northern France.

The [[Battle of Agincourt]] (1415) took place nearby.

